---
title: Easy Berbere & Honey Pork with Garlic & Herb Roast Veggie Toss
description: Meet our Berbere spice - a complex blend of peppers, cardamom, clove, cinnamon, fenugreek and coriander. It does an amazing
job in coating tender pork strips, making this meal all about the little differences. Along with a flavourful roast veggie toss and a
refreshing yoghurt drizzle, it'll sure become a household hit!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
